{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Bible Puzzle</strong> is an educational and relaxing game, perfect for all ages, from children to adults. Designed as an excellent option for family leisure, the game offers difficulty levels starting from just 4 pieces, allowing even the youngest players to have fun and learn while assembling biblical scenes.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As you start the game, players are invited to select a biblical image to assemble. Each image represents a significant passage from the Scriptures, and upon completing the puzzle, short clips are shown to tell the story behind the image, providing an educational and uplifting experience.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">STORYTELLING:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each puzzle pack includes video stories that provide context about the images in the pack.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175310/extras/Storytelling.gif?t=1736830260\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">CLICK &amp; SWAP:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Click on one piece, then click on a second piece to swap their positions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175310/extras/Click_and_Point.gif?t=1736830260\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">DRAG &amp; DROP:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Simply drag a piece to swap it with any other piece.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175310/extras/Drag_and_Drop.gif?t=1736830260\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">ACHIEVEMENTS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unlock achievements by completing specific challenges, enhancing engagement and fun.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175310/extras/Achievements.gif?t=1736830260\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">KEY FEATURES:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Various difficulty levels:</strong> Choose the ideal challenge level for yourself or your children, with options ranging from just 4 pieces to many more, adapting to the player\u2019s skill level.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Global and friend rankings:</strong> Engage in healthy competition with friends and players worldwide. Each image has its own ranking, encouraging repeat play and improvement.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Inspiring background music:</strong> Enjoy melodies inspired by the poetic books of the Bible, such as Job, Psalms, Proverbs, Ecclesiastes, and Song of Songs, creating a calm and introspective atmosphere while you play.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Regular content updates:</strong> New additional content will be released periodically as DLCs, offering new images and biblical stories to explore and assemble.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Educational experience:</strong> Beyond being fun, the game also offers a learning opportunity about biblical stories, making screen time more meaningful.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Bible Puzzle</strong> is more than just a game; it\u2019s a fun and educational way to explore the Scriptures as a family, ensuring that both you and your children are engaged in a safe and enriching activity. Download now and start assembling these beautiful biblical stories!</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Discover Us on Steam","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3175310/88aca45c0e8d801da1d3c5f31a11bdf619056a6e.jpg"},{"name":"Discover Us on Google Play Store","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3175310/b2897cb13ce4c212be8e60c0b952298d794905c7.jpg"},{"name":"Discover Us on App Store","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3175310/d71e177029fd611e52648